## Instance setup

Set up the instance via environment variables.

### GitHub Authentication

If you are using a personal access token, set these variables:

- `GH_TOKEN`

If you are using a GitHub App, set these variables:

- `GH_APP_ID`
- `GH_APP_PRIVATE_KEY` — Base64 encoded contents of the PEM file

### Contents Repo

- `GH_REPO` — The name of the repository to use as data source for the wiki. Example: creatorsgarten/contentsgarten-wiki